Package GUI

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommandPanel
    Class that represents GUI for command panel, a text area where commands are processed and sent to the specified Arduino reference.
    Driver
    Main Driver for ValveGUI class
    ImagePanel
    Class that represents GUI for image panel containing graphic and buttons to toggle specific valves.
    Pair
    Class to represent a pair of two doubles.
    SetupGUI
    Consists of the GUI and logic for a setup program used to initialize the image and the button count and locations in the image panel in the ValveGUI class.
    ValveGUI
    Main GUI class for the program.
    VideoControlPanel
    Panel that contains controls for video feed
    VideoPanel
    Panel to render video feed as series of images into JPanel
